Privacy Policy
Last Update: May. 20, 2022.
This Policy aims at informing you of the following
								content which might be involved in using GLIZA:
Our collection and use
									of your personal information
Our sharing, transfer
									and public disclosure of your personal information
Our protection of your
									personal information
